KitKat::

She looked up at Cooley and awaited an answer.
She had to refocus her optics as she had found her mind wandering 
again to Blackfang. Now was not the time to dwell on lost, lost 
crushes or cravings. Now she was setting herself to be in command of 
a group again. She hoped that with hard work, she would again rule 
over a group of predacons and bring them to victory over the 
maximals. Which was her spark's fondest wish  for her everntual 
future. She refocused her optics and looked at Cooley.
